<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h2">Debug File</bridgehead>
<para>A Debug File (DebugFile) parameter appears on the ODBC tabs of the OpenLink Client Configurator and the Administrative Assistant&#39;s Edit Data Sources Wizard utility.
 A DebugFile parameter also occurs in the [UDBC] section of udbc.ini.
 If you pass the full path to a file to Debug File, ODBC trace output will appear in the file.
 Leave Debug File blank, if you do not want to incur tracing overhead.</para><para>See Also: Trace </para></section></docbook>